. cdist-config
set -eu

__prompt()
{
   echo "Press enter to continue or ctrl-c to abort"
   echo "[Enter]"
   read answer
}

cat << eof

Welcome to cdist-quickstart, the interactive guide to cdist!

After you press enter, I'll create the basic directories for you.

eof
